query: SELECT fm.propertyId, p.addressLine1, dso.ds_probate as probate FROM familyMembers fm LEFT JOIN properties p ON fm.propertyId = p.id LEFT JOIN deepSearchOverview dso ON fm.propertyId = dso.propertyId GROUP BY fm.propertyId, p.addressLine1, dso.ds_probate;
